'From Squeak3.7beta of ''1 April 2004'' [latest update: #5972] on 16 July 2004 at 4:44:09 pm'!"Change Set:		deprFixSM-mdDate:			16 July 2004Author:			Marcus DenkerSmall fix for SM: SMInstaller class>>forPackage:directory: uses deprecatedExplanation:which is deprecated. This cs just patches the method to use #deprecated: instead "!!SMInstaller class methodsFor: 'deprecated' stamp: 'md 7/16/2004 16:42'!forPackage: aPackage directory: aDirectory	"Deprecated. Kept for backwards compatibility. Installing	a package means installing the latest available release."	self deprecated: 'Method Deprecated: Use SMInstaller>>forPackageRelease: instead. A directory is not needed in SM2, it has its own cache.'.	^self forPackageRelease: aPackage lastRelease! !